    <briefdescription>
<para>Class for making mesh from regular distance map. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>distance for each lattice of map is defined as point on ray from surface point cloud to direction point cloud, with length equal to 1/distance from distances file (if distance in file == 0 ray had no point) Generated from class <computeroutput><ref refid="classMR_1_1RegularMapMesher" kindref="compound">MR.RegularMapMesher</ref></computeroutput>. This is the non-const half of the class. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
